opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 1st day of February, 2010, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Application for an Immediate Hearing on the Pending Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
